The formula in the image can be written in LaTeX as follows:

```latex
\documentclass{article}
\usepackage{amsmath}

\begin{document}

\[
M = \frac{1}{2} (\lambda_{\text{max}} - \lambda_{\text{min}}) I - L.
\]

\end{document}
```

This LaTeX code will produce the same equation as shown in the image.

